{
  "message": "Fix sidebar icon border bleed, configurator overflow, and vite TS errors (#4390)\n\n* Fix sidebar icon border bleed, configurator overflow, and vite TS errors\n\n- Add bg-background to sidebar collapse/pin icon buttons so the Demo\n  Mode banner border doesn't bleed through their transparent backgrounds\n- Add overflow-hidden and truncate to Configurator strategy card metrics\n  so TTFT/Throughput text doesn't spill outside card boundaries\n- Add @types/node and tsconfig.node.json to fix 20 \"cannot find name\"\n  TS errors in vite.config.ts (IDE-only, build was unaffected)\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* Fix mission empty state button layout \u2014 stack icons above text\n\nChange the \"Start Custom Mission\", \"Browse Community Missions\", and\n\"Mission Control\" buttons from horizontal icon+text to stacked layout\nwith larger icons (w-5 h-5) centered above text. This fixes the\ndisproportionate icon sizing when text wraps to multiple lines.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* \ud83d\udc1b Fix @types/node version to ^22.0.0 and add allowJs to tsconfig.node.json\n\n- Align @types/node to ^22 to match CI Node version (20/22)\n- Add allowJs:true so JS config files (tailwind/postcss/eslint) are\n  included in the tsconfig.node.json project and benefit from Node typings\n\nSigned-off-by: github-actions[bot] <github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>\n\nAgent-Logs-Url: https://github.com/kubestellar/console/sessions/f565a90f-b151-4c10-b034-056acad06d96\n\nCo-authored-by: clubanderson <407614+clubanderson@users.noreply.github.com>\n\n---------\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: copilot-swe-agent[bot] <198982749+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>\nCo-authored-by: clubanderson <407614+clubanderson@users.noreply.github.com>",
